---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="For Agencies">
    <main>
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>For Agencies: Pioneer the Future of Legacy Representation</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Unlock unprecedented revenue streams through digital estate management and posthumous talent representation</p>
        </div>

        <section class="content">
            <div class="info-card vision">
                <h2>The Vision</h2>
                <p>In an industry constantly seeking new revenue opportunities, agencies now face a revolutionary frontier: comprehensive management of deceased performers' legacies. "Living with the Ghost of Sam" offers a blueprint for agencies to establish leadership in this emerging market, creating sustainable revenue while preserving and enhancing entertainment history.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card unique-concept">
                <h2>A New Agency Division with Massive Potential</h2>
                <p>Far beyond traditional posthumous representation, digital legacy management represents an entirely new category of agency businessâ€”one with diverse revenue streams, technological partnerships, and cross-platform opportunities.</p>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3>Key Business Opportunities</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Formalized estate representation contracts with revenue-sharing models</li>
                        <li>Technology licensing agreements for authorized digital recreations</li>
                        <li>Rights management across emerging platforms and technologies</li>
                        <li>IP development based on established performer personas</li>
                        <li>Educational and archival licensing programs</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card market">
                <h2>Built-In Multi-Generational Revenue</h2>
                <div class="two-column">
                    <div>
                        <h3>Immediate Revenue Streams:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Performance licensing for digital recreations</li>
                            <li>Archival footage enhancement and licensing</li>
                            <li>Documentary and supplemental content</li>
                            <li>Merchandising and consumer products</li>
                            <li>Series participation and consultation fees</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Long-Term Value Creation:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Ongoing royalty streams from new performances</li>
                            <li>Library value enhancement through renewed relevance</li>
                            <li>Tech partnership equity opportunities</li>
                            <li>Creation of new derivative intellectual property</li>
                            <li>Development of cross-platform legacy presence</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card advantages">
                <h2>Agency Advantages</h2>
                <p>Beyond revenue, establishing an estate division offers strategic benefits:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>First-mover advantage in an emerging high-value representation category</li>
                    <li>Enhanced relationships with current talent by offering lifetime legacy management</li>
                    <li>Creating synergy between contemporary and historical talent rosters</li>
                    <li>Developing valuable partnerships with technology companies and platforms</li>
                    <li>Building institutional knowledge and systems before competitors enter the space</li>
                    <li>Positioning your agency as the natural home for future estate clients</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card marketability">
                <h2>Market Position & Potential</h2>
                <p>The opportunity exceeds traditional posthumous representation:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>$45M+ total addressable market for comedy legacy representation by 2025</li>
                    <li>250% average increase in catalog value after successful digital recreation</li>
                    <li>15+ new revenue streams available through comprehensive legacy management</li>
                    <li>Growing consumer interest in nostalgic content with contemporary relevance</li>
                    <li>Potential to establish industry-standard contracts and deal structures</li>
                    <li>Synergistic relationships with streaming platforms seeking differentiated content</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card estate-roster">
                <h2>Priority Estate Acquisition Targets</h2>
                <p>Based on our development process, these estates represent particularly valuable partnership opportunities:</p>
                <div class="estate-grid">
                    <div class="estate-card">
                        <h3>The Sam Kinison Estate</h3>
                        <p>Central to our series concept with significant unrealized potential and passionate fan base spanning multiple generations.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="estate-card">
                        <h3>The John Belushi Estate</h3>
                        <p>Iconic physical comedy perfectly suited for digital recreation with substantial unreleased material and cross-media potential.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="estate-card">
                        <h3>The Gilda Radner Estate</h3>
                        <p>Groundbreaking female comedian with enduring cultural relevance and strong potential for contemporary reintroduction.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="estate-card">
                        <h3>The Chris Farley Estate</h3>
                        <p>Beloved physical comedian with significant unrealized potential and strong nostalgic appeal across demographics.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="estate-card">
                        <h3>The George Carlin Estate</h3>
                        <p>Philosophical comedian whose material maintains contemporary relevance with substantial archival content.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="estate-card">
                        <h3>The Richard Pryor Estate</h3>
                        <p>Revolutionary performer with cultural significance and substantial unrealized licensing potential across platforms.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card materials">
                <h2>Available Materials</h2>
                <div class="materials-grid">
                    <a href={`${base}scripts`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Series Scripts</h3>
                            <p>Full episodes demonstrating legacy integration</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}estate-model`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Estate Agreement Models</h3>
                            <p>Template contracts and negotiation frameworks</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}revenue-projection`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Revenue Projections</h3>
                            <p>Detailed financial models for estate representation</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}tech-partners`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Technology Partners</h3>
                            <p>Vetted partners for digital recreation implementation</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card contact">
                <h2>Build Your Agency's Legacy Division</h2>
                <p>Schedule a confidential consultation to explore how your agency can lead in this emerging representation category.</p>
                <a href="mailto:contact@example.com" class="contact-btn">Request Agency Consultation</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    main {
        color: white;
    }

    .hero {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('/living-with-the-ghost-of-sam/images/SamImage.jpg') no-repeat center center;
        background-size: cover;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .content {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
    }

    .info-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .info-card h2 {
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .info-card h3 {
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .info-card ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .info-card li {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .highlight-box {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .highlight-box h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .two-column {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .estate-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .estate-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .estate-card h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .materials-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .material-link {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
    }

    .material-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition: transform 0.2s, background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .material-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .contact {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .contact-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #2196F3;
        color: white;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .contact-btn:hover {
        background: #1976D2;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .two-column, .estate-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .materials-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>
